{"type":"message","id":"60a10c89","parentId":"19f23689","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:00:00.494Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:c57780c3-46fc-4d3b-aa73-56e1d17916b1 每日0点：备份 + 复盘] 执行每日任务：\n\n## 1. 备份\ncd ~/.openclaw && git add -A && git commit -m \"Backup: $(date +%Y-%m-%d)\" && git push origin main\n\n若 push 失败（secret 检测等），记录报错但继续。\n\n## 2. 复盘\n读取 memory/ 目录下的日志文件，进行内省分析：\n- 回放当日会话记录\n- 对比 MEMORY.md 基线\n- 识别理解偏差、低效操作、用户纠正点\n\n沉淀与调整：\n- 更新 MEMORY.md（提炼通用教训）\n- 按需微调 AGENTS.md 或 TOOLS.md\n\n输出简报（中文）：\n- 备份状态\n- 今日教训\n- 配置变更（如有）\nCurrent time: Tuesday, March 3rd, 2026 — 4:00 PM (UTC)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772553600484}}
