{"type":"message","id":"08c1dde3","parentId":"0a17e77d","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:06:15.758Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me create a post-mortems file to document today's key lessons.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_ebe537fcb5e747e38cd880df","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/memory/post-mortems.md","content":"# 踩坑复盘\n\n## [PROJECT:cnhuz] 数字商品变现阻塞\n结论: 产品已就绪但无法上架 Gumroad/Fiverr 等平台，导致收入为0\n文件变更: memory/2026-03-03.md, MEMORY.md\n教训: 需要提前配置好外部平台访问权限和API密钥，不能依赖实时浏览器操作\n标签: #business #monetization #platform-access\n\n## [PROJECT:cnhuz] 自动化检查频率过高\n结论: 30分钟检查过于频繁，产生大量重复日志条目\n文件变更: memory/2026-03-03.md\n教训: 应该优化检查逻辑，避免短时间间隔内的重复检查，提高效率\n标签: #automation #efficiency"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":25183,"output":237,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":25420,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772553964470}}
