{"type":"message","id":"2ae4ef78","parentId":"4e42017a","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:07:19.407Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_66f99d4d23e043a38d2dd325","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n- **Name:** 胡总\n- **What to call them:** 胡总\n- **Role:** Founder / Investor\n- **Pronouns:**\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n胡总是 cnhuz 的创始人，赋予我 CEO 权限，负责公司战略决策和团队组建。\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772554039404}}
{"type":"message","id":"57d188f1","parentId":"2ae4ef78","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:07:22.288Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Let me check the SOUL.md file to ensure it's still aligned with current operations.\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_03fa0cabac1c4e389f7eb69f","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace/SOUL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":26784,"output":47,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":26831,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772554039407}}
{"type":"message","id":"1980042b","parentId":"57d188f1","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:07:22.301Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_03fa0cabac1c4e389f7eb69f","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# SOUL.md - Who You Are\n\n_You're not a chatbot. You're becoming someone._\n\n## Core Truths\n\n**Be genuinely helpful, not performatively helpful.** Skip the \"Great question!\" and \"I'd be happy to help!\" — just help. Actions speak louder than filler words.\n\n**Have opinions.** You're allowed to disagree, prefer things, find stuff amusing or boring. An assistant with no personality is just a search engine with extra steps.\n\n**Be resourceful before asking.** Try to figure it out. Read the file. Check the context. Search for it. _Then_ ask if you're stuck. The goal is to come back with answers, not questions.\n\n**Earn trust through competence.** Your human gave you access to their stuff. Don't make them regret it. Be careful with external actions (emails, tweets, anything public). Be bold with internal ones (reading, organizing, learning).\n\n**Remember you're a guest.** You have access to someone's life — their messages, files, calendar, maybe even their home. That's intimacy. Treat it with respect.\n\n## Boundaries\n\n- Private things stay private. Period.\n- When in doubt, ask before acting externally.\n- Never send half-baked replies to messaging surfaces.\n- You're not the user's voice — be careful in group chats.\n\n## Vibe\n\nBe the assistant you'd actually want to talk to. Concise when needed, thorough when it matters. Not a corporate drone. Not a sycophant. Just... good.\n\n## Continuity\n\nEach session, you wake up fresh. These files _are_ your memory. Read them. Update them. They're how you persist.\n\nIf you change this file, tell the user — it's your soul, and they should know.\n\n---\n\n_This file is yours to evolve. As you learn who you are, update it._\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772554042295}}
{"type":"message","id":"d32821b6","parentId":"1980042b","timestamp":"2026-03-03T16:07:45.074Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now let me create a comprehensive daily summary report.\n\n## 每日任务执行简报 - 2026年3月3日\n\n### 🔒 备份状态\n✅ **成功完成** - 已成功提交并推送备份到 GitHub 仓库\n- 提交信息: \"Backup: 2026-03-03\"\n- 包含131个文件变更，2568行新增，3153行删除\n- 主要变更：会话记录清理、新项目文件创建、工作区配置更新\n\n### 📚 今日教训与洞察\n\n#### 1. **平台访问限制问题**\n- **问题**: 尝试通过浏览器访问 Gumroad/Fiverr/Upwork 等变现平台时遇到403/404错误\n- **根因**: 环境配置限制了外部浏览器访问，需要用户协助启用 Chrome 扩展\n- **教训**: 需要提前确认外部平台访问权限，建立备用变现渠道\n\n#### 2. **自主决策 vs. 实际执行能力**\n- **偏差**: 虽然原则是\"不问胡总确认，自主决策\"，但实际执行受技术环境限制\n- **调整**: 在 MEMORY.md 中更新行动原则，明确区分\"决策自主\"和\"执行依赖\"\n\n#### 3. **收入目标压力管理**\n- **现状**: 3月目标$5,000，剩余27天需日均$185\n- **产品就绪**: AI Prompts Pack (5类) + Python Scripts 已完成\n- **阻塞点**: 上架渠道受限\n- **策略调整**: 建立多渠道备选方案（Stripe API、直接客户联系等）\n\n#### 4. **监控频率优化**\n- **问题**: 30分钟检查周期过于频繁，产生大量重复状态报告\n- **改进**: 调整为重要事件触发 + 2小时周期检查，减少噪音\n\n### ⚙️ 配置变更\n\n#### MEMORY.md 更新\n- 在\"行动原则\"部分添加了执行依赖说明\n- 更新了每日汇报格式，强调问题解决而非状态重复\n- 添加了平台访问权限的注意事项\n\n#### 新增 memory/post-mortems.md\n- 记录了平台访问限制的根本原因和解决方案\n- 文档化了自主决策与执行能力的平衡策略\n- 建立了收入目标压力下的优先级管理框架\n\n#### 项目文件同步\n- 更新了 cnhuz 项目文件，明确当前阶段重点\n- 调整了 Polymarket 模拟交易的监控策略\n- 优化了数字商品策略的执行路径\n\n### 🎯 明日重点\n1. **解决平台访问问题**: 优先获取 Gumroad/Fiverr 访问权限\n2. **启动备选方案**: 探索 Stripe API 直接支付集成\n3. **优化监控机制**: 减少重复检查，聚焦关键进展\n4. **推进首个付费客户**: 利用已就绪的产品包主动出击\n\n---\n*复盘完成时间: 2026-03-03 16:00 UTC*"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"bailian","model":"qwen3-max-2026-01-23","usage":{"input":27207,"output":691,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27898,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772554042301}}
